There is The Beetle Barn just off of I-77 south of Cambridge, Ohio.  I went
there quite a few times in the late '80s and early '90s for parts for my '81
Rabbit, no long gone, and my '72 Westy, which I still have.  According to
Bing, it is still there.

I also went to a parts lot called Coynes which was located east of
Kirkersville but after looking, at the satellite pictures, it appears to be
no longer in operation.  It's across US 40 and west of the race track.

Brad Spear
'72 Westy
Burnsville, MN

